Name: TIGER TRIBE Activity Pack - Monster and Aliens
Description:
Keep the kids happy while out and about with these new, super compact Activity Packs.

Available in two designs, the packs each have 24 pages of engaging activities that you can take anywhere and everywhere, because there is no mess. Monsters & Aliens - with 24 pages of fun activities to choose from including colour mazes, finish the picture' and colour by numbers (all themed around the silliest bunch of creatures youve ever seen) and six coloured markers  you wont hear a peep from the back seat!

These sets come neatly packed in a self-contained, slide out box. Designed for easy portable play, the compact Activity Packs are a must-have item for when mum and dad need some time out at the cafe or when travelling.

They also make a great birthday gift for school friends too!

Each set contains: 24 pages of activities 6 coloured markers Handy storage box

Suitable ages 4+

Name: TIGER TRIBE Transfer Magic-Unicorns
Description:
Create some magic with two new additions to Tiger Tribe’s Transfer Magic activity sets - where kids use their imagination to make their own creative combinations. 
 
Transfer Magic is a super easy crafting activity that you can take anywhere, because there is no mess. Simply select a transfer sheet, remove the backing paper, position the selected image, face down on the background card and rub it using the pencil included.
 
Five unicorns just waiting for you to help them become the most beautiful unicorns in the world! Apply butterflies and bows, flowers and feathers and beautiful sparkling jewels or any combination you like.
 
Everything comes neatly packed in a self-contained, slide out box. Designed for easy portable play, the Transfer Magic packs are a must-have item for when mum and dad need some time out at the cafe. And perfect for keeping little hands busy when travelling. Great birthday gift for school friends. 
 
Each set includes:
  • 5x colour background cards
  • 4x sheets of colour transfers
  • 1x rubbing pencil
  • Handy storage box
Suitable ages 3+

Name: TIGER TRIBE Activity Pack - Pet Pals
Description:

Name: The Marble Hand
Short description: An incense holder shaped like hands that are inspired from Jean Cocteau's 1946 black & white movie. Made from sustainable marble powder.
Description:
Marble Hand Incense Holder The Marble Hand is a unique incense holder inspired by Jean Cocteau's 1946 black & white movie, where hands magically appear from the chateau walls in La Belle et Le Bête. This incense holder is made from sustainably sourced marble powder transported from Carrara, Italy and handmade with loving hands in France. Place a single incense stick in this beautiful marble hand index finger, light them up, and let it burn until it extinguishes. Perhaps, you should pair it with Maison Balzac's amazing incense range for best use! The Marble Hand incense holder dimensions
  • Height 17cm
  • Width Approx 6.2cm
  • 2mm wide holes to welcome the base of any incense stick
  • Incense is sold separately
This Maison Balzac product is handmade individually. This may result in slight differences between shapes, sizes, and colours. However these variances are part of the products' beauty! It will not deter the overall aesthetic and ability of the product as well.
Tags: gifts, Incense, incense holder
Meta: ingredients: Made from marble powder from Carrara, Italy
Meta: how_to:
COMPOSITION AND CARE

Wipe this product with a damp cloth or hand wash it with a soft bristle brush to keep it clean. Don't use strong alkali soaps as it could damage the glass. Handle with care to avoid glassware from breaking.

Always place the incense in a holder on a stable heat resistant surface out of reach of flammable objects while in use. Ensure the incense's ash lands on a non-flammable surface as it can discolour the furniture or create a risk of fire. Clean up only after the ash has completely died out. Do not leave burning incense unattended or move the incense once lit.

Keep out of reach from children, pets and away from draughts. Burning incense will create smoke: please ventilate the space after use.

Keep the wick in an upright position after extinguishing the flame

Keep away from draughts or flammable objects

Keep out of reach from children and pets

Don't leave it burning without supervision. Do not burn more than 2 hours at a time. Blow out candle before flame reaches 2cm from base.

Always lit in a well ventilated space and not flammable surface. Not suitable for outdoor use.

Meta: how_to:
Drops may be given directly into the mouth or added to daily water dish/food.

For acute conditions, the effects can be immediate. For long standing issues, allow 2 weeks of daily use to see results.

CAN MY PET TAKE MORE THAN ONE FORMULA AT A TIME?

No. Giving more than one formula at a time lessens the effectiveness. First Aid Kit is the exception and can be given as needed.

HOW DO I GIVE DIFFERENT FORMULAS TO PETS WHO SHARE A WATER DISH?

In this case, the remedy should be given directly into the mouth.
